  "category": "Uncategorized",
  "description": "Add Custom Logo from External Image Source\n\nIntegrate the specified image as the application logo by fetching it from https://wesolenutki.eu/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/dzieciaki-wektory.png\n\nRequirements:\n- Download and save the image locally to the project assets folder\n- Add the logo image to the appropriate location in the UI (header, navigation bar, or landing page)\n- Ensure proper sizing and responsive behavior across different screen sizes\n- Add alt text for accessibility\n- Optimize image if needed for web performance (compression, format conversion)\n- Consider fallback behavior if external image becomes unavailable\n- Update any existing logo references to use the new image\n\nTechnical considerations:\n- Verify image format compatibility (PNG)\n- Check licensing and usage rights for the external image\n- Ensure image loads correctly on different devices and browsers\n- Maintain aspect ratio to prevent distortion",
